  "remarks": "Nina Shastak is a Belarusian judge of the Brest Regional Court. She was appointed by Aliaksandr Lukashenka. She issued sentences against a number of citizens of Belarus who voiced their opinions against the Belarusian regime’s authorities. She also considered appeals against sentences of peaceful demonstrators, confirming those sentences.",
